The paper discusses the development of a deep network based on Tucker tensor decomposition and its application in image classification problems. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
